reviewText: The video was well done and the music sounds good.  I liked one or two songs only.  I thought I would like them all.  I'm just now getting to like this type of music genre, because I really like Pesado's desde la cantina.  This is a lot different.
calidadde sonido poeria ser mejor pero esta bien creo yo pero me gusto y si lo recomendaria a mis amigos
